name: Faith
description:
Militias from myriad of kingdoms joined in a war against a mysterious enemy who has mastered Alchemy and formed what seems to be an insurmountable foe:

A fluctuating sky fortress, that combines the power of fire, earth, metal, stone and wood elements utilized as power source, defense, and weaponry.


High quality art print using water and fade resistant inks presented on 220 gsm white matte paper with grain. - 21 cm x 29.7 cm (8.5″ x 11.5″) paper - 1.5 cm x 2.1 cm (0.6″ x 0.8″) border - 18 cm x 25.5 cm (7″ x 10″) printed area Limited run of 10 Each print is signed, numbered, and dated by the artist. The logo visible on the preview will not be on the print. The print will be posted with hardback envelope. - All UK postage: Royal Mail First Class Recorded £3.00 - All Europe & Rest of the World: Royal Mail Airmail Letters £6.00
